Package wobani.core

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChildContainer
    Contains a GameObject's children.
    Component
    All of a GameObject's Components based on this abstract class.
    ComponentContainer
    Contains all of a GameObject's Components.
    ComponentLists
    Stores Components in user defined lists.
    GameLoop
    The engine's main game loop.
    GameObject
    Represents an entity which has it's own position, Mesh or any other properties, you should create a new GameObject.
    GameObjectContainer
    Stores all the GameObjects.
    RenderableContainer
    Stores all the RenderableContainer.
    Scene
    Scene contains all the GameObjectContainer, the RenderableContainer, unique lists of Components and parameters like the main Camera or the main DirectionalLight.
    Time
    It computes the delta time factor and the frame per sec value and other useful values.
    Transform
    Stores a GameObject's transformation data.
